Director of Property Management
Ref:AR260701
Salary: Negotiable
Location: Middle East & North Africa, Abu Dhabi
Sector: Real Estate, Property Management
Date: 06 May 2014
Job type: Permanent
Our client is a subsidiary of a leading, UAE based Islamic bank. This well known and successful property consultancy within this high profile bank has developed a strong reputation within property management as well as valuation, project management and asset management and is well known for offering a tailored and professional service across its vast residential and commercial portfolio.
Due to growth within the business and a restructure within its parent company, our client is looking to hire a Director of Property Management. Based in Abu Dhabi, the successful individual will be responsible for overseeing a large team of property managers across 3 locations.
The successful Head of Property Management will have proven experience of:
Business developing and generating new clients on behalf of the business
Overseeing a team of property managers to include dealing with day-to-day management, appraisals and targets
Overseeing the management of over 20,000 units and 10,000 residential and commercial landlords based in Abu Dhabi
Overseeing facilities management
The successful head of department will have at least 3 years’ experience working in Abu Dhabi or the UAE at a similar level and at least 8 years’ experience working within property management. Ideally, applicants will have worked or be working in a bank and be able to speak Arabic although this is not essential.
Our client is offering progression and development within the business as well as affording the suitable individual the opportunity to work autonomously and lead a successful department.
Salary is flexible and dependent on level and experience.
Apply online or for further information, contact Azara Roger at Cobalt Recruitment on +971 2 611 3019.
